# 🌐 HTTP Methods

## GET

Used to retrieve data.

```text id="rest4"
GET /students
```

---

## POST

Used to create new data.

```text id="rest5"
POST /students
```

---

## PUT

Used to update existing data.

```text id="rest6"
PUT /students/1
```

---

## DELETE

Used to delete data.

```text id="rest7"
DELETE /students/1
```

---

## PATCH

Used for partial updates.

```text id="rest8"
PATCH /students/1
```

